          "activation_name": "Energized Blast",
          "effect": "You direct the stored energy into a short blast, targeting a creature within 15 feet. The target takes 2d10 force damage (DC 23 basic Reflex save).",
          "frequency": "once per 10 minutes",
          "links": [
